    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The WebSocket protocol enables two-way real-time communication between clients and servers.  This document specifies the use of Binary Floor Control Protocol (BFCP) as a new WebSocket subprotocol enabling a reliable transport mechanism between BFCP entities in new scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
